      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 💥 How to read — Misfires\nPer-cylinder **running totals**. A few scattered across a drive = normal noise.\n\n🚩 **One cylinder's line climbing steeper than the other three** = that cylinder's coil / plug / injector is failing. The **slope** and **one cylinder breaking from the pack** is the signal — not the absolute number."
      },
      "transparent": false
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Misfire accumulators (per cylinder)",
      "description": "Mode 06 accumulated misfire counts per cylinder. These are running totals — a rising slope, not the absolute value, signals a developing misfire.",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 10,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "postgres",
        "uid": "project300k"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "postgres",
            "uid": "project300k"
          },
          "rawSql": "SELECT timestamp AS time, misfire_acc_cyl1, misfire_acc_cyl2, misfire_acc_cyl3, misfire_acc_cyl4 FROM misfires WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp) ORDER BY timestamp",
          "format": "time_series"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "none",
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 0,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "showPoints": "auto"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "legend": {
          "showLegend": true,
          "displayMode": "list"
        },
        "tooltip": {
          "mode": "multi",
          "sort": "desc"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Latest accumulator per cylinder",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 14
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "postgres",
        "uid": "project300k"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": {
            "type": "postgres",
            "uid": "project300k"
          },
          "rawSql": "SELECT misfire_acc_cyl1 AS cyl1, misfire_acc_cyl2 AS cyl2, misfire_acc_cyl3 AS cyl3, misfire_acc_cyl4 AS cyl4 FROM misfires WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp) ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 1",
          "format": "table"
        }
      ],
